        public java.lang.String create()
        Creating entry template. Examples: 
         
 String tml1 = new TmlEntry(Level.INFO, "Hello, {}!", "log").create();
 // This code creating template:
 // [LEVEL INFO] [TIMESTAMP 2022-03-31T02:09:59.441] [CLASS org.viise.zhurnal.tml.TmlEntry] [MESSAGE Hello, log!]
